<h3>Generator Options</h3>

<ul>
  <li><code>--stimulus</code>: Generates a new Stimulus controller named alert_controller.js and registers it for enhanced interactivity</li>
  <li><code>--directory</code>: Customize the component location (defaults to <code>app/views/rui/components</code>)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Component Properties</h3>
<ul>
  <li><code>title</code>: Optional alert heading text</li>
  <li><code>icon</code>: Optional Heroicon name for alert icon</li>
  <li><code>dismissable</code>: Adds a close button when set to true</li>
  <li><code>classes</code>: Additional CSS classes for alert container</li>
  <li><code>content</code>: Alert message as string or block content</li>
  <li><code>color</code>: Theme color variants:
    <ul>
      <li>Base colors: <code>:primary</code>, <code>:secondary</code></li>
      <li>Status colors: <code>:red</code>, <code>:yellow</code>, <code>:green</code></li>
      <li>Extended palette: <code>:orange</code>, <code>:amber</code>, <code>:lime</code>, <code>:emerald</code>, <code>:teal</code>, <code>:cyan</code>, <code>:sky</code>, <code>:blue</code>, <code>:indigo</code>, <code>:violet</code>, <code>:purple</code>, <code>:fuchsia</code>, <code>:pink</code>, <code>:rose</code></li>
      <li>Neutral tones: <code>:slate</code>, <code>:gray</code>, <code>:zinc</code>, <code>:neutral</code>, <code>:stone</code></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>


